        <h3>Quality vehicles, quality descriptions</h3>
        <br>
        <p style="text-align: left;">It would be easy to say that we are bidding on used cars, damaged cars, vans and
            light trucks. But we do much more. We offer you peace of mind. Our descriptions include full details of the
            vehicle, damage reports and a complete photo gallery with images of the vehicle, as well as photographs of
            any damage. For many vehicles we even have external inspection reports. It gives you that very important
            sense of peace.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: left;">What if the car has a problem? You don't have to worry. We have developed a policy
            for resolving complaints that guarantees fast and correct resolution. You can find the full complaint
            handling policy in your account. Please be sure to read it before you start bidding!</p>
        <br>
        <h3>The road to reliable vehicles</h3>
        <br>
        <p style="text-align: left;">Do you want your car business to benefit from safe and reliable cars? Do you want
            to offer your customers the best quality at the lowest price? <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Register">Register Now!</a> And
            you'll be ready to start
            bidding right away! The road to reliable cars at good prices starts NOW!</p>
